      "content": "i get that, but i don't really have time to book an appointment with my doctor right now with all this studying. it's just an herbal supplement, right? like, it's not a pharmaceutical drug so it shouldn't really interfere with the sertraline, should it? i just want to take a small amount to help with the stress.",
